 my main hand. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=farlanderb>FarlanderB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/30/02 9:36:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4523.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cresc blades of luclin?</span><hr size=1> I have on.<br>
<br>
It's rather nice for dealing damage, not aggro at all unless your group only requires you do enough damage to hold aggro.<br>
<br>
The effect is Shadow. It's a buff that can be overridden by almost any cleric buff. Since I'm rarely without Aegolism, the buff never sticks. I'm told that buffing yourself in combat is aggro, although I can think of much more effective procs to use if your after aggro. <br>
<br>
I do use this weapon when I'm not the MT and trying to pump out as much damage as possible. I like to use the CBoL and a LSoEE (/gasp! rogue weapon!) when I'm dealing damage on a raid. <p>[62 Warlord]<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong> Farlander</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Human)<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->[33 Enchanter] <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong> Fainel</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (High Elf)<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--> [10 Paladin]<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong> Sabern</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> (Half Elf)<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.guild-legerdemain.com">Legerdemain</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gartogggamorean@thesteelwarrior>Gartogg Gamorean</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/30/02 10:57:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4523.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cresc blades of luclin?</span><hr size=1> I use a seb croaking dirk which has the same ratio but no proc and think it performs quite well.  I picked the croaking dirk over the blades because the dirk has 4ac and is half the price on my server. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=cslochraven>CSLochraven</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 299<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/1/02 12:25:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4523.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://gs.cdnow.com/graphics/COVERART/local/L/80/01/00138001.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cresc blades of luclin?</span><hr size=1> They aren't bad.  They used to be a lot better before the Shadow proc got nerfed and now is overridden.  I really don't know anything about you (level, other gear, etc), but I used them shortly and they weren't too bad.  Not my first choice, though. <p>&lt;b&gt;Lochraven&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;<br>
Warlord&lt;br&gt;<br>
The Nameless<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aren31>Aren31</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 39<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/2/02 10:41:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4523.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Cresc blades of luclin?</span><hr size=1> I use a CBOL with a Frosty, I find better aggro with Frosty in Main Hand cause of more frequent Procs, but the damage is ok. I'm currently trying to find a good 1hs or 1hb I can afford because piercing is capped at 240, and I feel a slasher/basher would be a better weapon.  Fleshgrinder is my goal, or epics. I'm a Golem Raid and Dok Raid away.<br>
<br>
Cbol is a good fast weapon, but I'm not liking it's aggro-ability in the main hand. <p>Aren Steelblade&lt;BR&gt;<br>
Warlord of the Chimera&lt;BR&gt;<br>
Saryrn</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=4523.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=4523.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4523.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=4523.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=4523.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4523.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=4523.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriorthearena">The Arena<option value="thesteelwarriorthebattlefield">The BattleField<option value="thesteelwarriorthebunker">The Bunker<option value="thesteelwarriorthetavern">The Tavern<option value="thesteelwarriorfrm6">The K